prod.desciption: The women's Air Jordan 1 High Seafoam (W) arrives in a smooth white leather construction with Seafoam Durabuck overlays and Swooshes. On the laces, crisp bronze trimming stands out against the design's subtle coloration. The women's Air Jordan 1 High Seafoam (W) released in August of 2021 and retailed for $170.
